{"tid":416150,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"＊[劣圖]小藍毒撚Roselia耳機SE-MX8-K開箱","createTime":"2017-09-27T14:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T14:52:01.000Z","uid":58038,"like":12,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"95f0e43df16f79210df2c399b5aabf857ef32c83","tid":416150,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的 識小藍既都知<br />\n小藍呢排好撚鍾意Roselia呢隊野<br />\n早排公佈話合作款耳機出 小藍緊係即刻出哂水狗沖去訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信呢對由Pioneer出既SE-MX8-K, 毒少少買開周邊野/玩開耳機既都知呢對咩黎<br />\n就係標準公廁毒撚款<br />\n同過好多作品合作 有LoveLive!, 黑子籃球, 超時空要塞&Delta;之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n音質包膠就最後先講 貼下劣圖先 6s+手震影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得傷眼可以出返去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220338_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220338_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=c41192a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n岩岩到手影返張相先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  d啪啪紙留返得閑拎黎啪下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220338_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220338_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=a7f276f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=288d6592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有一半都係拎黎買呢個濕鳩膠架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_d0096ec6c83575373e3a21d129ff8fef.jpg&h=80cb30cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於到個盒<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_032b2cc936860b03048302d991c3498f.jpg&h=9f5db541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_18e2999891374a475d0687ca9f989d83.jpg&h=8e7f3188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_fe5df232cafa4c4e0f1a0294418e5660.jpg&h=e69c8f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個盒係就咁推出黎就係 開頭仲諗緊邊到開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_8cda81fc7ad906927144235dda5fdf15.jpg&h=8aba812f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_30e62fddc14c05988b44e7c02788e187.jpg&h=8ef559e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_ae566253288191ce5d879e51dae1d8c3.jpg&h=69f8b455&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n耳機個保護套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個用途其實就唔係拎黎保護耳機既 用途可以參考下冰川紗夜既聲優 工藤晴香既ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/BZao9xmjUcn/?taken-by=kudo_a.k.a_910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBZao9xmjUcn%2F%3Ftaken-by%3Dkudo_a.k.a_910&d=8su28JN39u2ivKGf5Dmse26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=355eeeea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBZao9xmjUcn%2F%3Ftaken-by%3Dkudo_a.k.a_910&h=b92ef362\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/BZao9xmjUcn/?taken-by=kudo_a.k.a_910</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">工清又贏!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_62bf1edb36141f114521ec4bb4175579.jpg&h=eae413ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盒入面既內容<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_8df7b73a7820f4aef47864f2a6c5fccf.jpg&h=d10300cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全set野係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_9414a8f5b810972c3c9a0e2860c07532.jpg&h=19daa8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一半係買個架 一半係買左呢個面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/220339_edab7ba7e203cd7576d1200465194ea8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F220339_edab7ba7e203cd7576d1200465194ea8.jpg&h=23ed4204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後補張我家下用緊既設備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n音質方面我就好少用呢d耳牛耳罩 <br />\n對上一隻用都係得隻msr7可以比較下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人就覺得真係好一般d聲 唔值2萬5羊呢個價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過可能係未煲開 岩岩拎出黎聽 過幾日聽耐左到時再包膠吧<br />\n但相信買得呢d耳機既人都對音質冇乜研究吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw qc真係好撚垃圾 隻耳機岩岩一拎出黎聽 即刻發現條線插頭有d接觸不良<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...遲下先再攪攪去<br />\n但係多數都係就咁擺係到做擺設算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後想講 Roselia呢隊野真係好撚高質 原唱曲好,翻唱曲都有一定水準既<br />\nlive亦都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我中毒個首歌係live翻唱個時既魂のルフラン<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vclUU-6Ewao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvclUU-6Ewao&d=8su28JN39u2ivKGf5Dmse26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=851c0b95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vclUU-6Ewao</a><br />\n但到家下最鍾意既歌一定係熱色スターマイン<br />\nlive個時真係型撚到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gS8YBL06JbU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgS8YBL06JbU&d=8su28JN39u2ivKGf5Dmse26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e1d3e3c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gS8YBL06JbU</a>"},{"pid":"596ace49ad6a09fe58069fb73495bb7fb7b1cc1b","tid":416150,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0ca744d51d114142ad7c6eb95d0330f471dc4c","tid":416150,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:20:24.000Z","msg":"負皮左，自己反省下"},{"pid":"61805fb5ddea46cc9b5338a924b744334b99eb05","tid":416150,"uid":59911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負皮左，自己反省下</blockquote><br />\n負皮左，自己反省下"},{"pid":"e10ea4b31d0fa52d0afc429c55ed1ede46bd66b0","tid":416150,"uid":58038,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"待奏狗唔收你地皮唔撚得"},{"pid":"fbac5682c3f624cbc7ef49834b26efb43da6e8c8","tid":416150,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"支持藍莓清‼️"},{"pid":"829e0daffea51210e49c6023427856e31467f439","tid":416150,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>待奏狗唔收你地皮唔撚得</blockquote><br />\nG持"},{"pid":"336b63c31647f96dfd767cd53f56e2e5f6b542fa","tid":416150,"uid":59911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:25:33.000Z","msg":"成班話支持<br />\n但負皮7:0 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8c4c439b5d523b0dc3bd051a9f79f8f81fcd103","tid":416150,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:26:30.000Z","msg":"牙藍買左幾$$"},{"pid":"58cb6b46ade0f141ea0b32fbf12769f79d5f8503","tid":416150,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牙藍買左幾$$</blockquote><br />\n你未正皮喎"},{"pid":"2e9c8b268791f1370e19750fa5c8385c7eef5